Sour Cream Icing
via Amy Zirkle (courtesy of the internet)

4 tablespoons butter, softened
1/2 cup sour cream
1/2 teaspoon vanilla extract
1/2 teaspoon lemon juice
1/4 teaspoon salt
2 3/4 cups confectioners' sugar

In a medium bowl, mix together the butter, sour cream, vanilla, lemon juice
and salt. Stir in confectioners' sugar, and beat with an electric mixer until
smooth.
